headline: Nasdaq Announces Mid-Month Open Short Interest Positions in Nasdaq Stocks as of Settlement Date May 15, 2025
summary: NEW YORK, May 27, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- At the end of the settlement date of May 15, 2025, short interest in 3,168 Nasdaq Global MarketSM securities totaled 13,735,568,588 shares compared with 13,300,707,903 shares in 3,156 Global Market issues reported for the prior settlement date of April 30, 2025.
